WEBVTT

00:00:02.712 --> 00:00:07.087
un mir hobn geredt az it hot khasene gehat mit ayer froy,

00:00:06.643 --> 00:00:08.814
ya. ya ya.

00:00:07.087 --> 00:00:07.987
Lea.

00:00:08.584 --> 00:00:10.974
un ir hot zi bagegnt in Yisroel,

00:00:10.525 --> 00:00:12.257
Yis- Yisroel, yo, in Rekhovot.

00:00:11.554 --> 00:00:13.185
oyf a khasene.

00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:13.236
yo.

00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:16.475
dertseylt undz a bisele vegn ayer froy.

00:00:18.169 --> 00:00:28.153
vos hob ikh tsu redn tsu dertseyln. m'hot zikh bakent, ir veyst dokh vi yunge khevre, un m'iz gegangen aroys a tsayt biz mir hobn geheyrat. mir hobn nisht geheyrat bald tsu morgns, s'hot genumen a yor anderthalbn.

00:00:28.513 --> 00:00:35.358
m'iz gegangen aroys yedes mol ven ikh hob gehat CHOFESH bin ikh gekumen arayn keyn Rekhovot un m'hot farbrengt m'iz gegangen un un m'hot geheyrat nakher.

00:00:35.263 --> 00:00:37.265
ven hot ir khasene gehat?

00:00:37.390 --> 00:00:41.889
in eyn u- eyn un fuftsik.

00:00:42.283 --> 00:00:43.509
in eyn un fuftsik?

00:00:43.127 --> 00:00:43.964
ya.

00:00:45.422 --> 00:00:49.618
hot ir a mol dertseylt ayer froy ayer iberlebenishn fun der tsayt fun der milkhome?

00:00:48.426 --> 00:00:54.613
o ya o ya, zi veyst ales. un ikh hob zi gefirt oykh keyn Oyshvits, iz zi geven mit mir in Poyln mit mit zeks yor tsurik.

00:00:54.822 --> 00:01:03.203
hob ikh zi gefirt keyn Poyln un ikh hob ze gevezn ikh bin geven mit ir in Treblinke un ikh bin geven mit ir in Oyshvits, ikh bin geven iberal, un ikh hob ir gevizn mayn plats vu ikh bin geshlofn, vu ikh hob gegesn.

00:01:02.854 --> 00:01:04.502
ven zent ir geven in Poyln?

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:05.885
mit zeks yor tsurik.

00:01:05.858 --> 00:01:08.096
zeks yor tsurik, dos iz in vos a yor?

00:01:06.972 --> 00:01:10.746
yo, ya, ikh hob ni- ven di rusn zenen aroys. ikh hob zey shoyn mer nisht,

00:01:09.705 --> 00:01:14.053
no no, ikh meyn der yor vos ir zent gevezn dortn.

00:01:13.198 --> 00:01:14.086
ya?

00:01:14.076 --> 00:01:17.732
mit zeks yor tsurik, dos heyst in eyn un nayntsikstn yor?

00:01:17.704 --> 00:01:19.554
in NINETY eyn un NINETY.

00:01:19.982 --> 00:01:26.459
bin ikh gevezn dortn in Poyln, un ikh bin arayngeforn, ikh hob nisht mer gekent oyshaltn, ikh hob geshrign tsu mayn vayb, gib a kuk op, ikh bin geblibn lebn,

00:01:26.459 --> 00:01:33.662
far vos zol ikh nisht forn oyf keyver oves, zen dortn di gantse mishpokhe iz gevorn dortn oysgeharget in Treblinke?

00:01:34.647 --> 00:01:41.901
nu, un dos hot mikh gepaynikt, vayl sof kol sof yeder eyner do geyt oyf der UNK CEMETARY un m'geyt m'geyt un geyt aroyf

00:01:41.935 --> 00:01:48.914
tsum keyver un m- un m'zogt kadesh, m'hot a mol a yortsayt, un zog ikh, far vos az ikh bin geblibn lebn far vos zol ikh nisht geyn zen dortn ale?

00:01:49.041 --> 00:02:00.225
nu bin ikh arayngeforn, ze'mir geforn arayn keyn Treblinke, m'hot undz gevizn dem keyver oyf Treblinke. dos iz dos ershte mol vos in mayn lebn vos ikh hob gezogt kadesh barn keyver, ikh hob zikh gehat tsvey mol farkhalesht,

00:02:00.225 --> 00:02:03.407
m'hot mikh geratevet, ikh hob alts nisht gekent zogn,

00:02:03.407 --> 00:02:10.067
ikh hob nisht gegleybt zikh az s'vet oyskumen a tsayt ikh vel darfn zogn kadesh, s'kumt a tsayt m'darf zogn, ober nokh aza fal nokh di gantse FAMILY,

00:02:10.067 --> 00:02:13.577
di shvester un brider, di shvesters zenen geven mit kinder, brider mit kinder,

00:02:13.577 --> 00:02:21.772
un un un FAMILIES, un UNCLES, un ales, s'a veytik, m'farlirt azoy fil mentshn vos vos s'gevezn gebundn un geknipt.

00:02:23.685 --> 00:02:27.594
nu. ya, un ikh bin geven,

00:02:26.301 --> 00:02:29.552
un ayer gantse shtot yidn hot men genumen keyn Treblinke?

00:02:30.013 --> 00:02:32.622
di gantse undzer shtot iz gegangen keyn Treblinke.

00:02:32.697 --> 00:02:35.815
un dan nakher vayter iz geven nokh a zakh.

00:02:35.815 --> 00:02:39.862
ikh nakher ikh bin geven in Poyln, ikh bin geven in Treblinke,

00:02:40.003 --> 00:02:46.488
ikh bin tsurikgekumen fun Treblinke, in a shabes far nakht kum ikh arayn in hotel arayn, tref ikh a KVUTZA, a GROUP, fun Montreal,

00:02:46.488 --> 00:02:55.595
fun fun fun Dole Dezamur, di RABBI fun Dole Dezamur, vu di gantse khevre a khevre fun yidn fun Dola Dezamur hobn gemakht a GROUP, oykhet a

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.659
tsu zen Oyshvits, Treblinke,

00:02:57.659 --> 00:03:06.850
zogn zey, zey hobn shoyn gezen Treblinke. un eyner iz dortn geven tsvishn di yidn, eyner a LAWYER, vos er ken mikh, zogt er, Pinek, zog ter, vo- vo- vos tust du do? zog ikh, ikh bin do mit mayn vayb, er ken di vayb oykhet.

00:03:06.916 --> 00:03:11.891
hob ikh mikh zeyer shtark tsefreyt, hobn zey gezogt az zey forn morgn keyn Oyshvits.

00:03:12.808 --> 00:03:18.354
keyn Oyshvits VISITn. dos iz geven yidn vos zenen geboyrn gevorn do in Kanade, un zey forn mit dem RABBI.

00:03:18.917 --> 00:03:27.213
zogt er tsu mir, efsher vilstu geyn oyf shaleshudes? zog ikh, veystu vos? ikh ken arayngeyn oyf shaleshudes. vos iz do tsu redn? arayngeyn oyf shaleshudes, trefn zikh, mir veln redn a bisl.

00:03:27.473 --> 00:03:32.040
er iz avek, er hot gevust az ikh bin geven in Oyshvits. der zelber LAWYER.

00:03:32.181 --> 00:03:40.764
un geyt avek tsum RABBI, un dertseylt im, geb a kuk, ikh hob do, zogt er, a Montrealer yid, er iz geven in Oyshvits. un zey hobn tsu dorfn morgn forn di gantse GROUP keyn Oyshvits VISITn.

00:03:41.901 --> 00:03:45.439
iz tsugegangen der RABBI, zogt er tsu mir azoy, zogt er, Pinek,

00:03:45.833 --> 00:03:54.771
ikh volt gevolt, bay bay dem, azoy vi ikh bin arayngegangen ersht zey hobn dokh zayn shul, in hotel iz geven aza shul far yidn tsu davenen, un dort hot men gemakht shaleshudes. di resht iz geven shabes far nakht.

00:03:55.013 --> 00:03:59.510
kumt tsu der RABBI un zogt tsu mir, Pinek, ikh hob gehert, zogt er, dayn nomen, zogt er, er hot mir dertseylt mir,

00:03:59.566 --> 00:04:04.162
du bist gevezn a yid in Oyshvits, zogt er, ikh volt gevolt, zogt er, nokhn shaleshudes,

00:04:04.162 --> 00:04:08.844
oyb du kenst gebn a bisl a SPEECH. hob ikh gezogt, OK.

00:04:09.643 --> 00:04:12.236
er hot zikh derfreyt, nokh shaleshudes

00:04:12.242 --> 00:04:17.715
hot er mikh aroyf gerufn oyf zayn tish un er hot gemoldn der gantse khevre, mir hobn do, zogt er, a gast,

00:04:17.715 --> 00:04:23.036
zayn nomen iz Pinek Kreyndels, dos iz a yid vos hot ibergemakht, er iz a SURVIVOR fun Oyshvits,

00:04:23.194 --> 00:04:30.832
un er vet aykh ibergebn a barikht. hob ikh ongehoybn tsu dertseyln fun Oyshvits un ale lign, un zey hobn geklogt un geveynt un gekhalesht.

00:04:31.092 --> 00:04:39.101
ikh hob dertseylt fun alem, dos esn badingen, fun shlofn badingen, fun yeder zakh, vos iz tsugekumen, fun alding, un vi azoy ikh hob zikh bafrayt.

00:04:39.597 --> 00:04:47.387
nokh dem iz tsugegangen der RABBI, zogt er tsu mir, geb a kuk, reb Pinkhes, ikh vel dir gebn, zogt er, nokh a nomen, Pinkhes Khaim. zolst lebn eybik.

00:04:47.950 --> 00:04:55.386
du host mitgemakht azelkhes, der oylem iz shtark tsufridn. zogt er, yetst vet men khotsh visn vos s'hot dortn ongegangen, vos du host dertseylt,

00:04:55.493 --> 00:05:02.692
un hot zikh gebetn efsher ken men vayter mitforn, ikh zol vider zen, er vil mikh zen, er fort shpeter keyn Yisroel, zog ikh, mir forn oykh keyn Yisroel.

00:05:03.070 --> 00:05:07.012
zogt er az er vet forn arayn, donershtik fort er arayn keyn Yisroel.

00:05:07.457 --> 00:05:09.841
zog ikh, ikh for oykh avek keyn Yisroel.

00:05:09.841 --> 00:05:13.382
vil er er zol, vil er mikh aynladenen, er vet zayn in Yerusholaim,

00:05:13.437 --> 00:05:17.330
vil er ikh zol kumen tsu im in Yerusholaim. zog ikh gib a kuk on, mayn vayb hot di greste FAMILY in Yisroel.

00:05:17.330 --> 00:05:20.394
zeyer a groyse FAMILY, s'a por hundert mentshn.

00:05:20.434 --> 00:05:25.455
zog ikh, k- un zey hobn undz derzen. ikh ken avekforn fun zey tsu dir? du farsh- zogt er, derbarem dikh,

00:05:25.455 --> 00:05:31.391
kum arayn, zogt er, oyf shabes, s'vet zayn far mir aza fargenign, du vest haltn nor fraytik vestu zayn kum arayn, for avek shabes.

00:05:31.391 --> 00:05:35.701
ikh hob nisht gekent, ober er iz geven, er hot mir geshikt a PICTURE fun Oyshvits,

00:05:35.701 --> 00:05:37.765
hob ikh di PICTURE do fun Oyshvits,

00:05:37.765 --> 00:05:40.233
m'hot geshtelt lekhtlekh un er hot mir gedankt mir,

00:05:40.233 --> 00:05:44.467
un di khevre ven zey trefn zikh fun der gantser GROUP, nokh biz hayntikn tog, ven zey trefn mikh,

00:05:44.467 --> 00:05:48.966
Pinek, m'ken dikh nisht fargesn fun dayn SPEECH vos du host gegebn. dos iz eyns.

00:05:48.966 --> 00:05:56.889
tsu morgns vayter, iz iz got helft, hoyb ikh on tsu redn vayter, yo.

00:05:56.889 --> 00:06:03.662
in in in hotel. makht zikh vayter a rederay, fun dem fun yenem, dem fun yenem, vi azoy Poyln hot gehandlt,

00:06:03.904 --> 00:06:09.883
gib ikh mikh a shtel avek, un un demolts hob ikh shoyn gekent redn, s'nisht geven di rusn, m'hot shoyn geven fray, m'hot gekent redn.

00:06:09.883 --> 00:06:15.845
shtel ikh mikh avek un zog eyn zakh. iz geven a bisl polyakn. un yidn.

00:06:16.071 --> 00:06:23.349
zog ikh, ir veyst vu ir tret? yeder trit vos ir tret in Poyln iz oyf blut.

00:06:23.349 --> 00:06:29.297
der hotel vos mir zitsn yetst shteyt in geto, iz geven foyer der geto.

00:06:29.300 --> 00:06:35.087
do iz shteyn mir oyf blut. mir tretn yeder trit iz geven oysgegosn yidish blut.

00:06:34.954 --> 00:06:36.281
vi heyst der hotel?

00:06:40.405 --> 00:06:48.431
Forum. Forum. ikh bin gevezn in Forum, in Kroke bin ikh gevezn in in dos, in in HOLIDAY INN. der Forum.

00:06:48.792 --> 00:06:55.152
do ikh dos iz der Forum shteyt dort, ikh hob fotografirt di matseyve fun ir veyst dokh der denkmol fun der geto in Varshe.

00:06:55.152 --> 00:06:57.918
zog ikh, der hotel shteyt vu der geto iz gevezn.

00:06:57.918 --> 00:07:05.053
do hot gebrent fayer, do hobn zikh farbrent yidn, do iz gevorn fargosn liters shvere liters mit blutn.

00:07:05.143 --> 00:07:06.431
dos hot men getretn.

00:07:06.431 --> 00:07:07.835
un dos iz nokh nisht genug.

00:07:07.835 --> 00:07:13.516
un dos, ikh hob zey ongehoybn tsu dertseyln, vos ir hot getun do enkere milkhome, vos ir hot gearbet mit di daytshn,

00:07:13.516 --> 00:07:16.303
un dos vos ir hot getun nokh der milkhome,

00:07:16.703 --> 00:07:20.966
az ikh bin arayngekumen keyn Apt, ikh bin gekumen zen mayn bruder,

00:07:21.900 --> 00:07:26.011
iz hot gevezn dortn zelbn hoyz iz geven a hoyz fun dray shtok.

00:07:26.592 --> 00:07:34.393
oyfn tsveytn shtok hobn di yidn gevoynt, un oykhet in der zayt un der zayt gevoynt a froy a goye vos hot mikh gekent. oy! panye Pinko! panye Pinko!

00:07:34.393 --> 00:07:35.714
zi hot zikh derfreyt.

00:07:36.497 --> 00:07:45.029
hot zi mir gezogt mir, az ikh zol nisht shlofn di nakhtn dortn bay di yidn. zog ikh far vos? far vos zol ikh nisht hobn di yidn bay fal? zogt zi, Pinek,

00:07:45.373 --> 00:07:52.049
kum arayn tsu mir, ikh meyn nisht keyn shlekhts, nor kum arayn, shlof bay mir in hoyz, vestu zayn geratevet.

00:07:54.030 --> 00:08:00.386
bay nakht zenen gekumen di A.K. bafaln dos hoyz. un m'hot ongehoybn tsu klapn.

00:08:00.932 --> 00:08:04.063
un zi heyst mikh ontun, di froy heyst mikh ontun.

00:08:04.114 --> 00:08:09.390
oyb du kenst kum shnel aroys, vel ikh dikh aroysfirn oyf der hintn. zey zenen gekumen in fornt, iz do a balkon fun hintn.

00:08:09.390 --> 00:08:12.199
ir veyst aroptsushpringen oyfn hoyf un aroysgeyn oyf a tsveyter gas.

00:08:12.252 --> 00:08:17.919
hot zi mikh aroysgeyogt oyf der balkon, un ikh hob aropgeshprungen fun di balkon, fun tsveytn shtok,

00:08:17.976 --> 00:08:25.803
un ikh loyf aroys fun der anderer zayt iz geven a shmole gas s'ahingekumen fun der breyter gas. un ikh loyf oyf Ostrovtser veg un ikh khap a taksi UNK.

00:08:25.803 --> 00:08:27.403
UNK.

00:08:28.303 --> 00:08:36.430
un er fort, zogt er, UNK. zog ikh, UNK. vifl du vest mir zogn, for! ikh hob alts gemeynt m'vet mir nokhloyfn.

00:08:36.471 --> 00:08:42.382
un er fort avek mit mir keyn Ostrovtse. un zogt mir der prayz, ikh nem aroys un gib im nokh a gutn TIP, un firt mikh tsu, vu?

00:08:42.382 --> 00:08:44.787
fir mikh tsu, zog ikh, tsu der tsu der tsu der ban.

00:08:44.787 --> 00:08:53.678
er hot mikh tsugefirt tsu der ban, hob ikh dortn genekhtikt. genakhtikt, a por sho iz nokh gevezn oyf der ban, biz ikh hob bakumen der ban vos fort arayn keyn Tsozomir, zen dem bruder.

00:08:54.257 --> 00:08:55.921
dos iz geven demolts di nakht.

00:08:57.058 --> 00:08:59.617
un ikh hob gehaltn a SPEECH demolts in Varshe,

00:09:00.079 --> 00:09:02.725
hob ikh ze gegebn vos di A.K. hobn gemakht.

00:09:02.725 --> 00:09:05.350
hob ikh zey dermant zey, ver zent ir gevezn.

00:09:05.350 --> 00:09:12.300
ikh bin geforn in Tshekhn nokh der milkhome, oyf yeder stantsye hot men ayngehaltn di Royte Kreyts un meydelekh mit vayse fertekher

00:09:12.300 --> 00:09:14.400
mit milkh mit zeml mit puter,

00:09:14.400 --> 00:09:20.550
m'hot gezogt far di ALL far di imigrantn, far di farshlepte mentshn, vos m'hot zey geshlept, s'do mentshn

00:09:20.550 --> 00:09:24.600
vos zenen geven in lagern, zol men aroysgeyn nemen milkh mit zemelekh mit puter.

00:09:24.953 --> 00:09:29.351
ir hot oykh geheysn makhn puter, ir hot gegebn KADURIM, ir hot geshokhtn.

00:09:27.417 --> 00:09:29.335
in vos a shprakh hot ir geredt mit zey?

00:09:29.408 --> 00:09:30.532
poylish.

00:09:29.458 --> 00:09:30.414
tsu zey?

00:09:31.433 --> 00:09:36.694
in poylish. geredt a poylish, ikh hob zey gegebn, zenen geblibn shteyn, hobn zey dos nisht gehert keyn mol.

00:09:36.694 --> 00:09:40.744
zog ikh, ver iz geven der A.K.? vos hot ir getun? ir hot gekemft gegn yidn gegn daytshn,

00:09:40.744 --> 00:09:45.494
nokh di milkhome hot ir geshosn shvangerdike froyen, yidishe. avekgeharget yedn eynem.

00:09:45.494 --> 00:09:49.819
mikh hot ir gevolt avekhargenen, ikh bin antlofn bay nakht, zog ikh, aropgeshprungen fun tsvey shtok a FLOOR,

00:09:49.819 --> 00:09:52.719
un antlofn keyn Ostrovtse vi azoy m'hot geharget demolts fir yidn,

00:09:52.847 --> 00:09:56.722
in dem hoyz. akht iz geven, hot men fir geharget. fir hobn zikh oykh bahaltn.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:01.245
vi lang zent ir gevezn in Poyln oyf ayer bazukh?

00:10:01.082 --> 00:10:04.198
demolts bin ikh nisht geven lang, ikh bin nokh geven demolts, m'hot genumen dem bruder,

00:10:03.597 --> 00:10:05.059
no no no, yetst.

00:10:04.238 --> 00:10:07.657
yetst, yo, bin ikh gevezn dortn bin ikh gevezn akht tog.

00:10:08.068 --> 00:10:12.900
hob ikh genumen mayn vayb, un dortn ikh hob gedungen bald a taksi in Varshe,

00:10:13.026 --> 00:10:17.126
un ikh bin geforn di gantse akht tog bizkale ikh bin tsurikgekumen keyn Varshe,

00:10:17.126 --> 00:10:21.851
arayngegangen in hotel arayn, genumen dort di peklekh un aropgeforn nakher tsum PLANE un geforn keyn Yisroel.

00:10:21.851 --> 00:10:28.375
ikh bin in Yisroel vayter, ir veyst dokh vi s'iz in Yisroel, hob ikh gearbet, gedos un di ales getun,

00:10:28.375 --> 00:10:34.725
un m'hot gelebt, m'hot nokh oyfgeboyt zikh a sheyne hoyz in Yisroel, ikh hob gevoynt in a zeyer a sheyn hoyz oyfgeboyt zikh a BEAUTIFUL in Rekhovot,

00:10:34.725 --> 00:10:39.079
un m'hot gefirt a sheyn lebn, un un un un zet dokh azoy dos iz es.

00:10:38.140 --> 00:10:41.846
un a khuts di a khuts di armey vos far a basheftigung hot ir gehat?

00:10:41.785 --> 00:10:48.152
ikh hob gehat farshidene gesheftn, ikh hob gehat a gesheft un ikh hob gehat ikh hob gearbet, farshidene gesheftn hob ikh gemakht, ober,

00:10:48.152 --> 00:10:50.841
ikh hob gelebt. ikh hob gelebt sheyn. ikh hob gelebt sheyn.

00:10:49.750 --> 00:10:53.186
un un ayere khaveyrim, di gezelshaft vos ir hot gehat?

00:10:52.703 --> 00:10:57.000
o a gut gezelshaft. o hob ikh gehat a zeyer gut gezelshaft. ikh hob gehat eynem a khaver,

00:10:55.842 --> 00:10:58.688
a sakh nay gekumene, o amerstns hige?

00:10:57.853 --> 00:11:02.453
alts nay gekumene. alts nay gekumene. ikh hob a gezelshaft eyner vos hot gehat a KOLNOA,

00:11:02.592 --> 00:11:10.483
yo, hot men zikh getrofn tsuzamen, eyner vos hot gehat a fabrik fun tekstil, m- ikh hob gehat a gute CHEVRA, m'hot zikh getrofn yedn fraytik un shabes, un un afile in mitn der vokh.

00:11:10.236 --> 00:11:14.972
un ir hot gehat bakante oder khaveyrim vos es zenen geven hige geboyrn in Yisroel?

00:11:14.573 --> 00:11:20.810
ikh hob gehat bakante geboyrene, ober di MOST iz geven alts ayngevanderte. alts ayngevanderte frishe. fun Poyln.

00:11:21.205 --> 00:11:25.687
fun Poyln, Rumenyen, mir hobn zikh gehaltn tsuzamen. m'iz geven gute FRIEND.

00:11:26.368 --> 00:11:28.437
vi lang zent ir geblibn in Yisroel?

00:11:28.461 --> 00:11:30.227
ikh bin geven in Yisroel tsvontsik yor.

00:11:31.583 --> 00:11:36.049
ikh bin aroysgeforn zibn un zekhtsik, ven ikh hob geendikt di z- di di milkhome, di zeks-tege milkhome,

00:11:36.122 --> 00:11:40.503
ikh hob geendikt di zeks-tege milkhome un dos iz geven mayn letste milkhome. dray milkhomes hob ikh mitgemakht in Yisroel.

00:11:40.797 --> 00:11:43.930
un dos iz geven di sibe vos ir zent avek?

00:11:44.155 --> 00:11:53.500
