00:20:24.273 --> 00:20:30.902
vos zenen bagangen undzer folk un undzer mishpokhe un far undzere kinder, vos zey hobn opgetun,

00:20:30.975 --> 00:20:42.410
dos iz dokh nisht tsu bagrayfn. m'ken shraybn tog un nakht, m'ken shraybn bikher, m'ken dos nisht ibergebn vos zey hobn opgetun. dos iz gornisht gloyblekh.

00:20:47.479 --> 00:20:54.979
